Distribution channels also play a significant role in shaping the energy drinks market, with various options available to consumers for purchasing these products. Supermarkets/hypermarkets are a popular choice for buying energy drinks due to their wide product availability and convenience. Consumers can easily find a variety of energy drink brands in these retail outlets, making it a preferred shopping destination for many. Convenience stores also play a vital role in the distribution of energy drinks, particularly for impulse purchases where consumers may grab a drink on the go. Online retail has emerged as a growing distribution channel for energy drinks, offering consumers the convenience of ordering products from the comfort of their homes and accessing a wide range of options from different brands.

